library(lattice)
xyplot(df$Reaction ~ df$Days | Subject, df, type=c("g", "p", "r"),
       index=function(x, y) coef(lm(y ~ x))[1],
       xlab="Days of sleep deprivation",
       ylab="Average reaction time (ms)",
       aspect="xy")
